			   Product Descriptions
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
SHORT DESCRIPTION:
			 HEXXAGON - The Animated Strategy Game
		      Published by Software Creations (VGA/286/SB)

MEDIUM DESCRIPTION:
		      ** HEXXAGON - The Animated Strategy Game **
		      ** From Software Creations & Argo Games. **
		      Immerse yourself in one of the most enjoy-
		      able and richly crafted board games to
		      date. Over a MEG of animated 256 color VGA
		      graphics & digital sound make this game an
		      instant classic! 1-on-1 or play vs computer.
		      Req: VGA, 286 or above. SoundBlaster support

LONG DESCRIPTION:                      
		       Software Creations presents
	   Argo Games' HEXXAGON - The Animated Strategy Game

 Immerse yourself in one of the most enjoyable and richly crafted board 
games to date. Revel in the fully animated 256 color VGA graphics and 
completely digital sound. Sharpen your wits against CRANIAC, your 
unmerciful computer opponent. Alter the very state of matter!

 Play testers have called HEXXAGON "More addicting than Tetris." Get it, 
and find out why HEXXAGON is an instant classic!

 Features:
  o 256 color VGA graphics.
  o Digital sound effects for SoundBlaster and 100% compatibles.
  o Over a MEG of Graphics and Sound!
  o Play against a friend, or against the computer.
  o Fully functional shareware version.

 Requirements:
  286 or better.
  VGA compatible graphics card.
